{"tid":186611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死4隻]焚衣紙致山火　風向變燒死4滅火員","createTime":"2017-04-04T10:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T17:18:44.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f977eb6909d647cf906d356f5106fe0dfa43a8f7","tid":186611,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170404/bkncn-20170404150935775-0404_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170404%2Fbkncn-20170404150935775-0404_05011_001.html&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=471ac887\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170404/bkncn-20170404150935775-0404_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n清明時節，孝賢墓前拜祭先人，難免焚燒衣紙冥鏹供先人享用，惟山種引發山火時有發生。昨日中午12時40分，山西省內一名村民上山拜祭時因燃燒衣紙不慎引發山火，接報到場的4名滅火隊員，因現場風向突變而被捲入大火之中，最終被救出時因傷勢過重，經搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該場山火目前已經受到控制。經查，起火原因為溫家莊一名成姓村民上墳燃燒衣紙所引發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9082c9fe68ba532fc73cf5b072298309c3018891","tid":186611,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"燒野就會令先人收到，人講就信，傻鳩<br />\n港獨必須除去支那5千年搵笨習俗"}]}